Grandfather	Narrator
family relationship,guardianship,inheritance
The grandfather is the narrator's only known relative and raises them from birth until his death in 2009.<SEP>The narrator is raised by or connected to their grandfather, who gives them a letter before dying.

Letter	Narrator
possession,revelation
The narrator keeps the letter until their 27th birthday and opens it to learn the identity of their parents.<SEP>The narrator receives and later opens the letter, which reveals the truth about the time loop and their identity.

Boyfriend	Narrator
abandonment,identity,reunion,romantic relationship
The boyfriend is in a relationship with the narrator, abandons her in 2023, and reappears in 2027 after her surgery.<SEP>The boyfriend is revealed to be the narratorâ€™s future male self, forming a romantic relationship with their past female self.

Letter	Parents
identity revelation,information source
The letter contains information that reveals the identity of the narrator's parents.

Child	Narrator
identity,parent-child,parent-child relationship,separation
The narrator gives birth to a child in 2024, who is immediately stolen.<SEP>The narrator gives birth to the child, who is also a version of themselves, and later steals the child to return them to 2000.

Grandfather	Letter
instruction,message delivery,possession
The grandfather gives the narrator a letter before his death with instructions to open it on their 27th birthday.<SEP>The grandfather gives the letter to the narrator before dying, instructing them to open it at age 27.

2024	Child
abduction,birth
The child is born and abducted in 2024.

Narrator	Parents
family relationship,unknown identity
The narrator does not know their parents until opening the letter in 2027.

Grandfather	Masked Person
death,violence
The masked person kills the grandfather in 2009.

2000	Narrator
birth event,life cycle closure,time travel
The narrator is born in the year 2000.<SEP>The narrator returns to the year 2000 with the newborn child (their younger self) to complete the temporal loop by raising their past self.

2009	Grandfather
death event,timeline anchor
The grandfather dies in 2009 at the hands of a masked person.<SEP>The grandfather is killed in 2009 by the masked narrator, a pivotal event that sets the narrator on their destined path.

2023	Narrator
abandonment,pregnancy,romantic obligation,time travel
In 2023, the narrator becomes pregnant and is abandoned by her boyfriend.<SEP>The narrator travels to 2023 to initiate a relationship with their female self to ensure conception.

2027	Narrator
accident,reunion,revelation,surgery
In 2027, the narrator experiences a car accident, surgery, reunion with boyfriend, and revelation about parents.

Masked Person	Narrator
identity,time travel
The masked person is a future version of the narrator who kills the grandfather to preserve the timeline.

2000	Child
origin point,time travel
The child is taken back to 2000 by the narrator to restart the life cycle and close the time loop.

Narrator	Time Loop
causality,participation
The narrator is both subject to and responsible for maintaining the time loop to ensure their own existence.

27th Birthday	Letter
instruction,temporal condition
The letter explicitly instructs the narrator to open it on their 27th birthday, making this date a critical condition for its revelation.

2009	Narrator
pivotal event,time travel
The narrator travels back to 2009 to kill their grandfather as the masked person, ensuring the timeline proceeds correctly.

2024	Narrator
aging,realization
In 2024, the narrator recognizes their resemblance to their grandfather and completes the loop by returning the child to 2000.

Car Accident	Narrator
identity revelation,transformation trigger
The car accident causes the narratorâ€™s full transformation into a male and leads to the realization that they are their own boyfriend.

Gender Transformation	Narrator
identity,personal change
The narrator undergoes a gender transformation from female to male, which is both biological and tied to the time loop mechanics.
